CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 10, 1962, pg. 1. Portions of article read: "'Miss Universe' Title Sought By Pittsburgh Area Beauties - Pittsburgh area beauties now are signing up for the Miss Universe Contest for selection of Miss Pittsburgh.  Among the first entries were Velma Reed, 7625 Kelly St.; Alberta Thompson, 2332 LaPlace St., and Dolly Blairman, 3548 Webster Ave. Extension, all of the Marlene Moore Modeling Agency..."
TitMainTitle: Andrea "Shugie" Shepherd or Velma Reed modeling one-piece light colored bathing suit on coffee table or bench, for entry in the 1962 Miss Pittsburgh contest
